Author: BEDBulimic
Text: Not an alcoholic so I can't imagine how tough it must be for you, but this was relatable to a fellow depressed bulimic (me). It sounds like a rough spot for you rn, hang in there, we're all here standing behind you and rooting for you!   You've already done great by making a plan and knowing what you have to do. One step at a time. You've got this. Take care of yourself
